Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.39,0:02:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the pirates who are \Nafter the One Piece...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.69,0:02:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...head for the New World, the \Nsecond half of the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.03,0:02:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, no one has ever fully explored it
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.28,0:02:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,except for Gold Roger, King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.41,0:03:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The New World has ruined many \Npirates' dreams and ambitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.46,0:03:02.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Monkey D. Luffy,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.21,0:03:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a boy whose body turned to rubber \Nafter he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.66,0:03:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and his friends venture into that sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.05,0:03:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.42,0:03:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After surviving a fierce battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.60,0:03:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Straw Hats finally entered the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.98,0:03:25.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-- the harshest sea ruled \Nby the Four Emperors.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.90,0:03:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They landed on Punk Hazard;
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.51,0:03:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,an island with two parts, one \Nburning, the other frozen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.53,0:03:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy learned about the hideous experiments
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.54,0:03:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,performed by Caesar Clown, the Master,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.03,0:03:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and headed off to investigate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.62,0:03:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So the clan split up. However...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.00,0:03:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.63,0:03:46.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are footprints, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.13,0:03:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it an animal? If it's a \Nhuman, he must be a Giant.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.09,0:03:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sense something.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.61,0:03:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two beast-looking creatures.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.72,0:03:57.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're we gonna do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.43,0:03:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are they?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.56,0:04:01.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Law? The Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.23,0:04:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, we're on a snow-capped \Nmountain so it must be them!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.57,0:04:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Snow Mountain Killers - stalking \Nout from deep in the snowstorm!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.28,0:04:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Brownbeard, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.21,0:04:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your name is also on our kill list.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.02,0:04:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys, you didn't harm \Nmy friends, did you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.03,0:04:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Where did he go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.64,0:04:45.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They took Nami with them!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.15,0:04:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Save Nami! Luffy's Fight on \Nthe Snow-Capped Mountains!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.28,0:04:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They kidnapped Nami?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.03,0:04:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.54,0:04:57.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though they were very big,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.49,0:04:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't notice they were there until
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.67,0:05:01.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they appeared in front of my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.58,0:05:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, it was centaurs and now, beast men?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.45,0:05:06.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are a bunch of strange creatures here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.75,0:05:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe they were waiting for their \Nchance to attack us somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.92,0:05:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They didn't come here to save Brown-gator?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.80,0:05:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seemed like their main purpose \Nwas to kill us and take the kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.73,0:05:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But first, they killed Brownbeard \Nat the Master's command.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.46,0:05:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were supposed to be on the same side.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.48,0:05:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brownbeard admired him so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.32,0:05:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Master was our warm-hearted savior!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.70,0:05:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.95,0:05:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This Master guy is a very twisted person.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.54,0:05:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let these kids go \Nback to such an evil person!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.79,0:05:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't help worrying about \NNami in Franky's body, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.38,0:05:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't know what they're gonna do to her!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.59,0:05:55.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I'll get her back at any cost!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.24,0:05:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys, look after those kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.26,0:05:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.18,0:06:02.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my body that they took!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.18,0:06:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper, I can't fight like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.04,0:06:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me the bean that you \Neat when you transform
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.73,0:06:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,yourself into a monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.48,0:06:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a bean!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.55,0:06:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Rumble Ball is a power drug!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.74,0:06:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think you can control it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.66,0:06:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can handle it with my super spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.03,0:06:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just give it to me! There's no time to argue!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.62,0:06:27.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.05,0:06:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.59,0:06:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just one, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.05,0:06:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?! It was in this \Npocket the whole time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.22,0:06:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course it was. It's Chopper's.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.97,0:06:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen. You can become a monster \Nfor just three minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.10,0:06:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't fight after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.31,0:06:51.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So if possible, transform into Kung \NFu Boost like I did earlier and...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.07,0:06:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.28,0:06:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Buber!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.49,0:07:00.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's way too early!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.37,0:07:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Franky! This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.59,0:07:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why're you attacking me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.18,0:07:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! He's out of control as I thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.64,0:07:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So is there much point to Franky going?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.48,0:07:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After running wild, he won't \Nbe able to move for a while
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.75,0:07:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so he's not gonna be helpful at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.87,0:07:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Instead, he's going to be in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.28,0:07:44.47,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,CAESAR'S LABORATORY
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.49,0:07:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know where he got it but \Nthis "Cyborg" Franky guy has...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.37,0:07:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Vegapunk's laser weapon \Nmounted in his body.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.13,0:07:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make good use of Vegapunk's invention.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.82,0:08:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After I chop his body up and \Ntake the laser system out,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.68,0:08:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he will be useless. Get \Nthe incinerator ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.14,0:08:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.32,0:08:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on with the Navy \Nidiots who came to steal the ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.48,0:08:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.34,0:08:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We ambushed them successfully but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.45,0:08:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What are they?!\N--Humans?! No, horses?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.00,0:08:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.88,0:08:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't get beaten that easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.63,0:08:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look behind you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.63,0:08:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.89,0:08:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we come!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.52,0:08:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are more!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.06,0:08:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--This is no good!\N--Nowhere to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.73,0:08:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to change tactics!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.33,0:09:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's try to seize the ship in full force!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.28,0:09:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain-chan... I mean, Smoker-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.46,0:09:21.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The battle is out of control now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.78,0:09:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.18,0:09:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...we're having a hard fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.43,0:09:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.70,0:09:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have an idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.61,0:09:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.90,0:09:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're dealing with the Navy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.99,0:09:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the perfect opportunity to test it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.20,0:09:57.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's great! Let's do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.25,0:10:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Contact the centaurs who are on patrol now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.26,0:10:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.22,0:10:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell all the other soldiers \Nevacuate if they want to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.64,0:10:17.79,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,THE MOUNTAIN BEHIND THE LABORATORY
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.81,0:10:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go! Let me go, you fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.35,0:10:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with you guys?! You perverts!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.90,0:10:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you gonna do to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.29,0:10:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know I'm pretty and have a good figure
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.51,0:10:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so you couldn't help kidnapping me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.47,0:10:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this guy talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.84,0:10:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He must be a queer. That's cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.83,0:10:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna pay for this! \NLuffy won't tolerate it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.00,0:10:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you two get your asses kicked!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.01,0:10:48.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be quiet for a moment. Noisy \Npeople like you are...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.93,0:10:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Not cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.97,0:10:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the weapons that are \Nmounted in your body are...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.02,0:10:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.35,0:11:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we give them to the Master, \Nour reward will be...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.32,0:11:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...So cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.74,0:11:10.64,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ROCK
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.66,0:11:14.39,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,It's cold today as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.41,0:11:15.27,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,SCOTCH
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.29,0:11:18.19,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,My body's cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.21,0:11:20.32,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,THE SNOW MOUNTAIN KILLERS \NTHE YETI COOL BROTHERS
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.34,0:11:23.32,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Then put some clothes on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.34,0:11:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our rifles are like cannons to you people.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.30,0:11:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have poison gas canisters, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.32,0:11:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody can beat us because \Nwe don't show ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.97,0:11:35.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said your friend will come?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.73,0:11:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure he'll come. We \Nset a trap to lure him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.56,0:11:47.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People can't help following \Nfootprints in the snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.18,0:11:53.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Footprints! Footprints! How helpful!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.93,0:12:00.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are pretty easy to follow!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.58,0:12:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Franky, I said stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.65,0:12:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.88,0:12:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The footprints end there...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.14,0:12:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.14,0:12:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy and Chopper... No, Franky?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.81,0:12:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.99,0:12:32.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out! They're around!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.95,0:12:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we, Scotch?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.49,0:12:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! He didn't notice there \Nwas a cliff. He is so careless!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.90,0:12:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are spikes at the bottom!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.13,0:12:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Die in vain.\N--Get skewered by the Ice Spikes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.30,0:12:51.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Armament Hardening!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.24,0:12:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.05,0:13:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Gatling!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.03,0:13:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. He's a little \Ntrickier than the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.98,0:13:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those two from before!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.48,0:13:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Second Gear!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.42,0:13:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.13,0:13:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Jet...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.42,0:13:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Pistol!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.22,0:13:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jet...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.57,0:13:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Stamp!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.89,0:13:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're gone, again!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.56,0:13:52.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool. We know these mountains \Nlike our own backyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.33,0:13:58.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are so many places \Nthat we can hide ourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.91,0:14:02.48,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,THE BURNING LANDS
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.50,0:14:04.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.17,0:14:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The place that the Master mentioned.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.28,0:14:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a huge building.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.30,0:14:14.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it a warehouse?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.95,0:14:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's kind of eerie.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.14,0:14:25.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This door is the one, right? \NOkay, let me open it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.57,0:14:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's tight! Guys, give me a hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.44,0:15:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I heard something.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.04,0:15:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't hear a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.87,0:15:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, we've been told not to go \Nanywhere near here, haven't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.18,0:15:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it really okay to open it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.68,0:15:14.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Master was the one who told us \Nthat and he wants us to open it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.38,0:15:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't trust the Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.18,0:15:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, that's not what I meant!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.58,0:15:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then stop complaining and lend a hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.50,0:16:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They move so fast even though they're so big.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.35,0:16:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.56,0:16:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.92,0:16:23.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a dead-end for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.11,0:16:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Balloon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.33,0:16:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a waste to use this power only
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.89,0:16:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,defensively just letting the \Nbullets bounce randomly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.54,0:16:35.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what Rayleigh said.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.69,0:16:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said I should focus on redirecting
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.79,0:16:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,every single one of them \Nback with twice the force!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.11,0:16:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.70,0:16:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Fire Salute!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.83,0:16:50.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rock!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.79,0:16:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.82,0:17:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, Franky!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.84,0:17:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you struggling with him more?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.84,0:17:11.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My body's hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.67,0:17:16.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they having a falling \Nout now? Screw them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.84,0:17:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.48,0:17:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just see if you don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.93,0:17:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Icy mountains are filled \Nwith potential weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.75,0:17:34.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out! The tip of an \Nicy mountain is gonna fall!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.89,0:17:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! Franky! Look up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.64,0:17:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't get away from it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.01,0:17:45.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The other one is right there, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.43,0:17:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Choke on this KYP gas canister that \Nwill make you drunk in a second
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.57,0:17:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and drop dead like your friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.28,0:18:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He did something useful!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.41,0:18:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! That was great, Franky!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.99,0:18:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, enough already!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.80,0:18:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Third Gear!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.51,0:18:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.71,0:18:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Elephant Gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.73,0:18:41.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He used one of his most daring attack there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.15,0:18:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.24,0:18:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.12,0:18:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.32,0:18:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Franky and Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.24,0:18:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll ask Chopper to treat you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.84,0:18:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.07,0:18:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you. We know these \Nmountains like our own backyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.57,0:19:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't catch up with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.20,0:19:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.32,0:19:29.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.76,0:19:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just won't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.93,0:19:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can reach way farther than you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.62,0:19:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! He's like a monkey.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.92,0:19:46.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.30,0:20:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! Since it's a huge mountain \Nrange, it'd be a pain if I lose them!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.38,0:20:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.70,0:20:10.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're the free-loader--- \NTrafalgar Law, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.53,0:20:12.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad to see you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.51,0:20:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was chased by Straw Hat Luffy and...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.62,0:20:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Room.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.87,0:20:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.36,0:21:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard! What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.86,0:21:21.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Counter Shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.89,0:21:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.31,0:21:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Hey you, give me back my body!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.55,0:21:47.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.13,0:21:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.33,0:21:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Tra-guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.94,0:21:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you save Nami?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.92,0:21:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.23,0:22:04.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I came here to talk to you \Nabout something, Straw Hat-ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.60,0:22:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you arrived on \Nthis island by accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.97,0:22:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there is an important key \Nlying somewhere on this island
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.81,0:22:17.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that can wreak havoc in the New World.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.89,0:22:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are only two ways to \Nsurvive in the New World.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.66,0:22:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Either by living under the Four Emperors
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.78,0:22:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or going against them.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.80,0:22:36.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I guess you're not a kind of person \Nwho wants to work under someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.40,0:22:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I want to stay as a captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.49,0:22:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, we have to form an alliance!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.86,0:22:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.09,0:22:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An alliance?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.05,0:22:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you and I join forces, maybe we can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.49,0:23:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a plan...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.15,0:23:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to bring down one of the Four Emperors!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.20,0:23:11.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Law declares to defeat the Four Emperors.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.83,0:23:15.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami and the others can't help but be hesitant by the frightening details...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.74,0:23:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Luffy's answer surprises not only his crew,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.60,0:23:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but Law, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.59,0:23:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, Caesar was also setting
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.60,0:23:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a terrible plan in motion.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.39,0:23:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.81,0:23:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Formed! Luffy and Law's Pirate Alliance!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.69,0:23:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!
